Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.74,0:00:19.37,Default,Sayaka,0000,0000,0000,,You lied to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.37,0:00:23.87,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,I simply asked you to become a Magical Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:28.29,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,Though you could say that I left out some things.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.63,0:00:34.88,Default,Sayaka,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:36.89,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,Because you didn't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:40.89,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,Everything would have been fine if you hadn't found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:44.44,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,Even Mami never realized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.86,0:00:51.36,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like humans such as yourself are even aware of their souls to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.93,0:00:54.86,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,It resides in the firing of your neurons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.86,0:00:58.94,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,It's there in your blood and in the beating of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.64,0:01:02.44,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,If your body ceases to function,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.44,0:01:05.37,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,your soul will also cease to be{extinguish}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.37,0:01:09.25,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,In order to prevent that, I made your souls tangible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:12.13,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,I simply made them into something that you can easily hold on to and protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:16.38,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,I did all of this so that you could fight Witches more effectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.38,0:01:19.05,Default,Sayaka,0000,0000,0000,,I never asked you to do something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.94,0:01:23.31,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,You're not taking this seriously enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.24,0:01:30.99,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,For example, let's say that you were to be stabbed in the stomach with a spear...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.44,0:01:44.66,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,This is true pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:47.71,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,You're down for the count after just one hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:55.78,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,The only reason you were able to last as long as you did against Kyouko...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:58.51,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,...is because most of the pain was being blocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:02.72,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,This is possible because your soul and your body have been separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:06.48,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,That is the only reason you survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.87,0:02:17.49,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,After a while, you'll learn to completely block out the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.83,0:02:22.49,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,Although that would also dull your reflexes, so I wouldn't recommend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:26.89,Default,Sayaka,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why must we do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.89,0:02:31.50,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,Did you not have a wish you wanted fulfilled even if it meant a life of constant battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:34.50,Default,Kyubei,0000,0000,0000,,Hasn't it already been granted?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.08,0:04:24.24,Default,asdf,0000,0000,0000,,All rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.85,0:04:26.74,Default,asdf,0000,0000,0000,,Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:50.39,Default,Madoka,0000,0000,0000,,You already knew, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:54.86,Default,Madoka,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:05:00.40,Default,Homura,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody has ever believed me before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:03.44,Default,Madoka,0000,0000,0000,,Why would Kyubei do something so cruel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.73,0:05:05.91,Default,Homura,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't believe what he's doing is cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:09.66,Default,Homura,0000,0000,0000,,A creature like him has no concept of human values.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:14.29,Default,Homura,0000,0000,0000,,He'll just say that it's a fair price for a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:17.54,Default,Madoka,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:20.31,Default,Madoka,0000,0000,0000,,You saw what he did to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:24.55,Default,Madoka,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan only wanted to heal the one she loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:29.55,Default,Homura,0000,0000,0000,,You can't say that wasn't a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:32.81,Default,Homura,0000,0000,0000,,The impossible was made possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.13,0:05:36.59,Default,Homura,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Miki Sayaka were to spend her entire life taking care of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:40.31,Default,Homura,0000,0000,0000,,...he would never have been able to play again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:45.50,Default,Homura,0000,0000,0000,,Even an entire human life is not equivalent to a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:48.57,Default,Homura,0000,0000,0000,,But that's precisely what he's selling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:53.58,Default,Madoka,0000,0000,0000,,Will Sayaka-chan never be able to return to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:55.68,Default,Homura,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:58.12,Default,Homura,0000,0000,0000,,Give up on Miki Sayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:06:00.84,Default,Madoka,0000,0000,0000,,But Sayaka-chan saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.58,0:06:05.25,Default,Madoka,0000,0000,0000,,If she hadn't become a Magical Girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.25,0:06:08.09,Default,Madoka,0000,0000,0000,,both Hitomi and I would have died!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:11.10,Default,Homura,0000,0000,0000,,Don't confuse gratitude for responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:16.44,Default,Homura,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing you can do for her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:22.48,Default,Homura,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't feel any responsibility to her just because you don't want to feel accountable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:28.39,Default,Madoka,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you always so cold, Homura-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.04,0:06:30.49,Default,Homura,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:34.37,Default,Homura,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's because I'm no longer human.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:45.47,Default,Sayaka,0000,0000,0000,,How can I even face Kyosuke like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:48.47,Default,Kyouko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Blockhead. How long are you going to keep moping around for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:02.02,Default,Kyouko,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go for a walk. I have something to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:14.20,Default,Kyouko,0000,0000,0000,,So are you regretting having this done to your body?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:20.49,Default,Kyouko,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm pretty okay with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.49,0:07:24.71,Default,Kyouko,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless, I'm able to do what I want because of this power I've obtained.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.08,0:07:27.71,Default,Kyouko,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something you should be so upset over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:30.22,Default,Sayaka,0000,0000,0000,,In your case, I'd say you're getting your just desserts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:33.72,Default,Kyouko,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly. Just think of it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:37.72,Default,Kyouko,0000,0000,0000,,If you live only for your own sake, you're responsible for everything you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:42.10,Default,Kyouko,0000,0000,0000,,You've got no reason to be mad and nothing to regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:45.77,Default,Kyouko,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lot easier if you think of it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:08.05,Default,Sayaka,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you bring me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:11.67,Default,Kyouko,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:17.47,Default,Kyouko,0000,0000,0000,,You hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:30.19,Default,Kyouko,0000,0000,0000,,Never waste food in front of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This used to be my father's church.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.41,0:09:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was too kind and honest for his own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyday, he would cry as he read the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was seriously distressed over the state of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He believed a new doctrine was necessary for this new era.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was what he believed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he began preaching things that were not a part of the usual teachings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.82,0:09:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, everyone stopped coming to the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.44,0:09:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was even excommunicated from the main branch of the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one took my father's words seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To an outsider, it looked like some kind of weird cult.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how obvious the messages my father tried to convey,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,people would shun him everywhere he went.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had no food and no place to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hadn't said anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just different. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.77,0:10:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they would just take five minutes to listen to what he had to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they would understand that he wasn't wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...no one listened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.79,0:10:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was painful. I couldn't forgive them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that nobody would listen to him seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I asked Kyubei to grant my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wished that everyone would heed my father's words.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next day, people were coming from all over to my father's church.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The numbers increased so much it was startling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole while I did my best as a Magical Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how righteous my father's teachings were...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they couldn't do anything against Witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my turn to shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I worked hard like an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With one of us up on stage, and one of us in the back...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it felt like my father and I were saving the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.67,0:11:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my father found out about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he realized that people were coming because of magic rather than faith,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my father was furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.31,0:11:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He called me, his own daughter, a deceiving witch. {don't capitalize this kthx -xmts}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was out there fighting Witches every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when my father broke down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.52,0:11:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was quite the spectacle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He would drink himself silly every night as though he were possessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He eventually got everyone together and burned everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the only one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wish I made destroyed my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:12:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I made it without considering other people's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that it was a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a promise to myself back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I vowed never to use magic for the sake of another again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This power is only to be used for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miracles aren't free.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.53,0:12:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish for hope, you will send out an equal amount of despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.25,0:12:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are one and the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how the balance of this world is preserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you tell me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should change that willful attitude of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a life of just desserts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You live only for your own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so concerned about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We both started from a mistaken conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.86,0:12:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason for you to continue on the path you've chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:13:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You already paid plenty for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I think you should think about changing your ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see the differences between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I can see that you've started down the wrong path.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just sit and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I misunderstood you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't regret using my wish for another's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.31,0:13:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I regret my decision now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.55,0:13:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the feelings upon which it was based will be for naught.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.76,0:13:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.87,0:13:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I paid too high of a price.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If used correctly, this power is truly a beautiful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.73,0:13:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.96,0:13:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you get those apples?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you get the money to pay for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.99,0:14:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't say, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.69,0:14:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I can't eat that apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't make me happy at all to receive one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're Magical Girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no others like us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will fight in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't like it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.87,0:14:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're free to try and kill me like you did before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.04,0:14:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No hard feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.74,0:15:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Sayaka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I just had a slight cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.54,0:15:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Was Kamijo-kun already discharged from the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijo, are you doing all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It won't help if I just stay home all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm supposed to be walking without crutches next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:16:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should go say hi to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't greeted him yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a matter regarding love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been hiding something from you and Madoka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.77,0:16:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a long time now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've admired Kamijo Kyosuke-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would've thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.39,0:16:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Kyosuke sure is a popular guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:17:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and he grew up together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if I had to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say we just can't get rid of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really all?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will no longer lie to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.94,0:17:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-san, can you face your true feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a very important friend to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want this to turn into something bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've had your eye on Kamijo-kun for much longer than I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you should get first pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.36,0:17:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will confess to Kamijo-kun after school tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.45,0:17:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.83,0:17:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to make a choice that you won't regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.35,0:17:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to decide whether you want to tell him how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.39,0:18:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I come with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.56,0:18:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not worth your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a regret today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:19:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought, what if I hadn't saved Hitomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It crossed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm completely unqualified to be an ally of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.78,0:19:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can face Mami-san like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitomi is going to steal Kyosuke from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's nothing I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.09,0:19:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't ask him to hold me with a body like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't ask him to kiss me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.12,0:19:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.16,0:19:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel better after crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.76,0:20:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.24,0:20:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have Witches to hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're only watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.19,0:20:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's fighting a Witch tonight, not a familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.84,0:20:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should drop some Grief Seeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.26,0:20:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This won't be for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're letting her have your prey for that reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.44,0:20:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's losing already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.98,0:21:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.61,0:21:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bear to watch any more of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.68,0:21:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough. Why don't you rest for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.76,0:21:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me show you how it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.74,0:21:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!{added, TLC -masat}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interfere. I can handle this on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.91,0:21:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.70,0:22:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She couldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.55,0:22:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really true!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.56,0:22:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With a body like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.56,0:22:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I don't have to feel any pain at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.27,0:22:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.52,0:22:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.10,0:24:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be a different Magical Girl from all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.07,0:24:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.07,0:24:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need anything in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.64,0:24:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't use magic for my own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.11,0:24:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such an idiot. {also tittle of the next ep}
